title: Two-Ingredient Soda Cake
directions: Combine ingredients in a large bowl. Whisk thoroughly and transfer to a baking pan sprayed with nonstick spray; bake in the oven until a knife inserted into the center comes out clean. (Refer to cake-mix box for pan size and approximate bake time.)
ingredients: 1/12th of cake (1 slice): 171 calories, 3.5g total fat (1g sat fat), 301mg sodium, 34g carbs, <0.5g fiber, 19g sugars, 1.5g protein
Tagged: Dessert Recipes, Vegetarian Recipes, 5 Ingredients or Less
1 box moist-style cake mix (15.25 - 18.25 oz.), any flavor
One 12-oz. can no-calorie soda (club soda works too!)
